cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.DS, cs.SOC, cs.LG 

This paper discusses the application of link analysis algorithms for ranking bipartite graphs in information retrieval, social networks, and recommender systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Other likely categories include cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
